{"_path":"/crypto/post_kccrwyf0-en","_dir":"crypto","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Arbitrum TVL Surpasses $18 Billion","description":"Arbitrum has strengthened its position as the leading Layer 2 solution, crossing the $18 billion total value locked (TVL) threshold for the first time since early 2024. The 23% growth over the past two weeks is driven by renewed institutional interest and significant protocol migrations from the Ethereum mainnet.","lead":"Arbitrum strengthened its position as the Layer 2 leader with a 23% TVL increase over two weeks","rubric":"crypto","tags":["news","cryptocenter"],"author":"Editorial","date":"2025-07-09","cover":"/imported/post_kccrwyf0/cover.webp","translation":true,"lang":"en","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arbitrum"}]},{"type":"text","value":" has strengthened its position as the leading Layer 2 solution, crossing the "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$18 billion"}]},{"type":"text","value":" total value locked (TVL) threshold for the first time since early 2024. The 23% growth over the past two weeks is driven by renewed institutional interest and significant protocol migrations from the Ethereum mainnet."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"record-tvl-figures"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#record-tvl-figures"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Record TVL Figures"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"According to DefiLlama, Arbitrum's TVL reached "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$18.2 billion"}]},{"type":"text","value":", the highest figure since the network's peak in March 2024. The growth is primarily attributed to the expansion of major DeFi protocols on the network."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Leaders by locked assets:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"GMX"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - $1.8 billion"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Aave V3"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - $1.2 billion"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Uniswap V3"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - $987 million"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"technological-improvements"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#technological-improvements"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Technological Improvements"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The recent surge coincided with the announcement of the "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stylus"}]},{"type":"text","value":" upgrade, which allows developers to deploy smart contracts in Rust, C, and C++ alongside traditional Solidity contracts. This technological advance has attracted several high-profile projects, including a new RWA tokenization platform with initial deposits of "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$340 million"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"institutional-adoption"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#institutional-adoption"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Institutional Adoption"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Three major trading firms have moved a combined total of more than "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$2.4 billion"}]},{"type":"text","value":" in assets into Arbitrum-based protocols. The average transaction fee remains stable at "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$0.12"}]},{"type":"text","value":", significantly below Ethereum's average fee of "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"$2.80"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"layer-2-market-dominance"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#layer-2-market-dominance"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Layer 2 Market Dominance"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arbitrum maintains its dominance with approximately "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"42%"}]},{"type":"text","value":" of the total Layer 2 market share, up from 38% in December. The network processes more than "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2.1 million"}]},{"type":"text","value":" daily transactions."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"impact-on-the-arb-token"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#impact-on-the-arb-token"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Impact on the ARB Token"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The growth has had a positive effect on the performance of the "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ARB"}]},{"type":"text","value":" token, which has risen "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"31%"}]},{"type":"text","value":" over the past month. The current annual yield for ARB stakers reaches "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"8.2%"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"t